Using a Build Workflow.

We need a complex workflow to create React app because

1. Optimize Code
2. Use Next-Gen JavaScript Features.
3. Be More Productive
4. Use Dependency Management Tools like npm or yarn
5. Use Bundler .Recommended: Webpack
6. Use Compiler (Next-Gen JavaScript Features)
    Babel+Presets
7. Use a Development Server


To create React app.

1. Install Nodejs
2. npm install -g create-react-app
3. create-react-app appname
4. cd appname
5. npm start
6. It will start the development server

